    A specified object is a typed object all official attributes can be got from together.
    SpecifiedByClassName
    A specified by class name object is a specified object whose type is the simple class name.

    A specified by class name and one attribute object is a specified object whose type is the simple class name and that has exactly 1 attribute.

    A specified by one attribute object is a specified object that has exactly 1 attribute.
